234
00:13:36.108 --> 00:13:39.688
organizing center. You would expect in this type of imaging to see a

235
00:13:39.728 --> 00:13:43.528
separation of around 20 nanometers between the T cell

236
00:13:43.588 --> 00:13:47.248
and its target, and eventually, for at least a subset of cells, you'd hope to

237
00:13:47.348 --> 00:13:49.968
