238
00:13:50.228 --> 00:13:53.028
So the question is, could you do this with this type of imaging?

239
00:13:54.208 --> 00:13:58.088
And so here now let me show you what that dataset that we collected looks like, and

240
00:13:58.148 --> 00:13:59.848
