00:20:36.453 --> 00:20:40.384
And in this particular case, we're saying if we have two structures, we want

355
00:20:40.424 --> 00:20:40.464
to

356
00:20:41.284 --> 00:20:45.084
find those that are closest to each other if we allow only cell birth,

357
00:20:45.644 --> 00:20:49.364
cell death, or cell movement. And birth in this case can also be

358
00:20:49.384 --> 00:20:53.274
delivery from the vasculature. And so that kind of mechanical and sort of

359
00:20:53.324 --> 00:20:57.244
physical idea allows you now to build up

