00:42:00.164 --> 00:42:03.694
But the amazing thing is this is the only way that you can exhaustively

725
00:42:03.744 --> 00:42:07.384
map all of these STIC lesions in a whole fallopian tube.

726
00:42:07.784 --> 00:42:11.574
And with this, we could then go back and synthetically sample that

727
00:42:11.604 --> 00:42:15.374
fallopian tube and cut 2D H&amp;E images and estimate how

728
00:42:15.424 --> 00:42:19.324
likely is it using the existing clinical pipelines, they call it SEFIM, it's the

729
00:42:19.364 --> 00:42:21.244
