00:43:24.552 --> 00:43:26.392
has changed with application of AI.

747
00:43:27.632 --> 00:43:31.032
So I think like you saw in the last talk, the main

748
00:43:31.532 --> 00:43:35.332
methods applied to image tissue can be split into sectioning-based methods

749
00:43:35.492 --> 00:43:37.052
and intact methods.

