00:43:49.232 --> 00:43:52.072
If we split them in two, we can think of them as intact imaging and

754
00:43:52.172 --> 00:43:55.012
sectioning-based imaging. If we take one as an example,

755
00:43:56.412 --> 00:43:58.172
an intact imaging method may

