00:44:21.132 --> 00:44:24.352
You can image all the way down to single-cell level and even within the cells,

763
00:44:25.112 --> 00:44:28.912
and you maintain continuity. The fact that you don't cut these blocks means you can

764
00:44:28.992 --> 00:44:32.772
image, say, collagen filaments and quite subtle anatomy within the

765
00:44:32.832 --> 00:44:33.272
tissues.

